  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      ARDS is a severe disease, it's important to predict the incidence of ARDS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      From January 1 to January 31, 2012 and from January 1 to January 10, 2013 , all patients
      admit to the ICUs will be enrolled. The demographic characteristics, diagnosis, formerly
      medical history, Ventilator indications, Ventilator data, other respiratory treatments,
      weaning outcome and 28 day mortality will be recorded.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
